The set of .f90 programs here is a complete single sample

mcsq.f90 
single-sample metropolis calculation  for Laughlin nu = 1/m giving  coulomb energy, sq(q) 
(not the  projected structure factor s0(q))
and the strip occupation distributions for  different widths


z_function_m.f90
routines for the modified sigma function

wf_tools.f90
tools for Laughlon wavefunction


new_coulomb_m.f90
implementation of ("lowest-landau-level") coulomb intercation


mc_tools_m.f90
Metropolis, etc

ziggurat.f90
random number generator